(4, 1, 'Consultancy', 'consultancy', '<h3 class=\"title-txt\">GHDatafie Consultancy</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our partners help you to use data to tranform your business. We work with you to understand your goals and map up strategies to achieving them. Our expertise are in assiting firms in managing strategic and compex enterprise data management challenges in a practical and effective way.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 image_para\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5\"><img src=\"http://ghdatafie.com/images/idea.png\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7\">\r\n<p>We help you to practically gain insights from your data using both proven and innovative techniques</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h4 class=\"title-txt text-center\" style=\"font-size:28px;margin-top:40px;\">We offer the following of insight services</h4>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"agileits-services consultancy_service\">\r\n<div class=\"services-right-grids\">\r\n<div class=\"agileits-services\">\r\n<div class=\"services-right-grids\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3 services-right-grid \">\r\n<div class=\"se-top\">\r\n<div class=\"services-icon\"><a href=\"data_list.php?cat-id=oA==\"><img src=\"http://ghdatafie.com/admin/images/brand_images/brand_images_5.png\" /> </a></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"services-icon-info\">\r\n<h5><a href=\"data_list.php?cat-id=oA==\">Business Intelligence &amp; Analytics</a></h5>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3 services-right-grid \">\r\n<div class=\"se-top\">\r\n<div class=\"services-icon\"><a href=\"data_list.php?cat-id=nQ==\"><img src=\"http://ghdatafie.com/admin/images/brand_images/brand_images_2.png\" /> </a></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"services-icon-info\">\r\n<h5><a href=\"data_list.php?cat-id=nQ==\">Dashboarding &amp; Decision Support</a></h5>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3 services-right-grid \">\r\n<div class=\"se-top\">\r\n<div class=\"services-icon\"><a href=\"data_list.php?cat-id=nw==\"><img src=\"http://ghdatafie.com/admin/images/brand_images/brand_images_4.png\" /> </a></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"services-icon-info\">\r\n<h5><a href=\"data_list.php?cat-id=nw==\">Data Warehouse Optimization</a></h5>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3 services-right-grid \">\r\n<div class=\"se-top\">\r\n<div class=\"services-icon\"><a href=\"data_list.php?cat-id=nmQ=\"><img src=\"http://ghdatafie.com/admin/images/brand_images/brand_images_31.png\" /> </a></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"services-icon-info\">\r\n<h5><a href=\"data_list.php?cat-id=nmQ=\">Reporting &amp; Data Provisioning</a></h5>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"services-right-grids third_section\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<h4 class=\"title-txt text-center\" style=\"font-size:28px;margin-top:40px;\">Our approach helps clients Understand their data and Information Assets Faster</h4>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n<div class=\"service_discover_image\">\r\n<div class=\"discover_text\">Quality</div>\r\n<img class=\"service-img1\" src=\"http://ghdatafie.com/images/discover.png\" /> <img class=\"img-responsive service_icon\" src=\"http://ghdatafie.com/images/right-arrow-(1).png\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"show process_text\">Clearly defining and documenting processes in place &ndash; setting out how things<span class=\"morectnt\"><span style=\"display:none;\"> such as data quality reporting and data quality issue management should be handled. GHDatafie Consultancy Service can give you valuable assistance with your data quality issues, advice on available tooling , setting achievable targets and realising significant business benefit. </span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"showmoretxt\" href=\"\">Show More</a></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n<div class=\"service_discover_image\">\r\n<div class=\"discover_text\">Measure</div>\r\n<img class=\"service-img1\" src=\"http://g