(1, 1, 7, 'Wearable devices', 'Statista dossier on wearable devices', '<p>The dossier presents a range of statistics on wearable technology. The wearables market includes smart watches, smart wristbands, fitness &amp; activity trackers, smart garments and clothing as well as other wearables. The wearable devices dossier includes data on the market size, shipments, market share and consumer interest.</p>', 365.00, 97, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 65, 1, '2019-06-06 05:41:57', '2019-06-06 06:27:01'),
(2, 1, 6, 'E-commerce worldwide', 'Statista dossier about e-commerce worldwide', '<p>This dossier presents statistics and facts on the global online retail e-commerce market. It includes data regarding the global e-commerce market volume as well as information on digital shoppers and consumer spending, as well as mobile commerce and digital payments.</p>', 365.00, 105, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 55, 1, '2019-06-06 05:43:07', '2019-06-06 06:26:49'),
(3, 1, 6, 'Smartphones', 'Statista dossier about Smartphones', '<p>This dossier presents a range of statistics and facts about the global smartphone market. It includes chapters on the number of smartphone users and penetration rates, sales value of smartphones and unit shipments, as well as information on vendors/manufacturers&#39; market share and shipments. The dossier also encompasses statistics on the average selling price of smartphones, manufacturing costs, and smartphone operating systems.</p>', 365.00, 75, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 61, 1, '2019-06-06 05:44:10', '2019-06-06 06:26:35'),
(4, 1, 5, 'Electric vehicles worldwide', 'Statista Dossier about the global market for electric vehicles', '<p>This dossier presents graphs and tables about electric vehicles worldwide and in the United States. Focusing on production and sales, the publication also provides data on selected electric car manufacturers.</p>', 365.00, 45, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 67, 1, '2019-06-06 05:45:12', '2019-06-06 06:26:24'),
(5, 1, 4, 'Amazon', 'Statista dossier about Amazon', '<p>This dossier presents insights and statistics on e-commerce provider Amazon.com. It provides an overview of the company&#39;s financials as well as statistics on user demographics and behavior. Detailed information regarding Amazon Prime usage can be found in the <a href=\"https://www.statista.com/study/46515/amazon-prime/\" target=\"_blank\">Statista Dossier - Amazon Prime</a>.</p>', 365.00, 167, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 61, 1, '2019-06-06 05:46:28', '2019-06-06 06:26:11'),
(6, 1, 5, 'Apparel market in the U.S.', 'Statista dossier on the apparel market in the U.S.', '<p>This dossier has been compiled to provide statistical information about the apparel market of the United States. The dossier has been broken down into four categories: overview of the global apparel market, overview of the U.S. apparel, apparel segments, and leading companies.</p>', 365.00, 97, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 48, 1, '2019-06-06 05:47:16', '2019-06-06 06:25:57'),
(7, 1, 4, 'Indian Lok Sabha election polls 2019', 'Statista dossier on the 2019 Indian general election polls', '<p>This dossier presents graphs and tables on polling for the 2019 Indian parliamentary election. It offers an overview of opinion polls and public opinion on campaign issues in addition to what first-time voters thought and opinions on fake news affecting the voting.</p>', 365.00, 45, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 50, 1, '2019-06-06 05:49:25', '2019-06-06 06:25:45'),
(8, 1, 4, 'Karnataka', 'Statista dossier on the Indian state of Karnataka', '<p>This dossier presents a range of statistics and facts about the Indian state of Karnataka, delving into its economy, population, infrastructure and agricultural output. The study also focuses on data from the state&#39;s capital Bengaluru.</p>', 365.00, 58, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 60, 1, '2019-06-06 05:50:30', '2019-06-06 06:25:34'),
(9, 1, 3, 'Passenger transport in India', 'Statista dossier about passenger transport in India', '<p>This dossier presents data on passenger transport in India, with focus on the modes. The study delves into air, water, rail and road transportation.</p>', 365.00, 49, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 56, 1, '2019-06-06 05:51:22', '2019-06-06 06:25:22'),
(10, 1, 3, 'Lok Sabha elections 2019', 'Statista dossier on the parliamentary election in India in April and May 2019', '<p>This dossier contains data on the parliamentary elections of the lower house, the Lok Sabha in India held in April and May 2019. The study delves into information regarding party finances, demographics of candidates, voter turnout and opinions on the right to vote and its process.</p>', 365.00, 53, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 62, 1, '2019-06-06 05:52:46', '2019-06-06 06:25:08'),
(11, 1, 3, 'Automotive industry in India', 'Automotive industry in India - Statista Dossier', '<p>This dossier presents graphs and tables about the passenger car industry in India. Focusing on passenger car production and sales, it also provides data on selected car manufacturers and their market share in India.</p>', 365.00, 42, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 58, 1, '2019-06-06 05:53:37', '2019-06-06 06:24:57'),
(12, 1, 3, 'BRICS advertising', 'Statista dossier on advertising in BRICS countries', '<p>This dossier has been compiled to provide statistical information about advertising in BRICS (Brazil, Russia, India, China, and South Africa) states.</p>', 365.00, 87, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 44, 1, '2019-06-06 05:54:20', '2019-06-06 06:24:42'),
(13, 1, 2, 'Cyber crime in India', 'Statista dossier on cyber crime in India', '<p>This dossier has been compiled to provide statistical information about cyber crime in India, delving into its causes, the attitude Indians have towards such offenses, and its effect on organisations across the country.</p>', 365.00, 51, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 54, 1, '2019-06-06 05:55:03', '2019-06-06 06:24:18'),
(14, 1, 2, 'Analytics market in India', 'Statista dossier on analytics market in India', '<p>This dossier has been compiled to provide statistical information about analytics market in India. This dossier provides information regarding overview of analytics market in India, revenue generated by analytics market across India in different cities and sectors and average salary of employees working in analytics market across India</p>', 365.00, 55, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 43, 1, '2019-06-06 05:56:03', '2019-06-06 06:24:02'),
(15, 1, 2, 'Electricity in India', 'Statista dossier about the Indian electricity market', '<p>This dossier presents graphs and tables about the electricity industry in India. Focusing on generation and use, the study delves into the sources and sectors of power and how it is distributed geographically across the country.</p>', 365.00, 53, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 56, 1, '2019-06-06 06:04:26', '2019-06-06 06:23:31'),
(16, 1, 2, 'Beauty industry in India', 'Statista dossier about the beauty and cosmetics market in India', '<p>This dossier presents insights and statistics on the beauty industry in India. The paper provides an overview of the Indian cosmetics industry, including statistics on demand and trade in addition to revenues for segments within the market.</p>', 365.00, 49, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 45, 1, '2019-06-06 06:05:09', '2019-06-06 06:23:20'),
(17, 1, 2, 'Jewelry market in India', 'Statista dossier on jewelry market in India', '<p>This dossier presents a range of statistics and facts about the jewelry market in India, including market size, retail outlets and demand volume.</p>', 365.00, 53, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 42, 1, '2019-06-06 06:06:32', '2019-06-06 06:23:07'),
(18, 1, 2, 'Alcohol market in India', 'Statista dossier about the alcoholic beverages market in India', '<p>This dossier presents insights and statistics on the alcohol market in India. The paper provides an overview of the Indian alcoholic beverages sector, including statistics on the domestic market, consumer behavior, and health impact within the country.</p>', 365.00, 42, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 42, 1, '2019-06-06 06:07:37', '2019-06-06 06:22:54'),
(19, 1, 2, 'Private equity and venture capital outlook in India', 'Statista dossier on venture capital in India', '<p>This dossier has been compiled to provide statistical information on private equity and venture capital across India. It includes a general overview, top deals across the county and PE/VC investments in different sectors.</p>', 365.00, 55, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 48, 1, '2019-06-06 06:08:25', '2019-06-06 06:22:07'),
(20, 1, 2, 'Maharashtra', 'Statista dossier on the Indian state of Maharashtra', '<p>This dossier presents a range of statistics and facts about the Indian state of Maharashtra, delving into its economy, population, infrastructure and agricultural output. The study also focuses on data from the state&#39;s two main cities - Mumbai and Pune.</p>', 365.00, 54, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 51, 1, '2019-06-06 06:09:54', '2019-06-06 06:22:41'),
(21, 1, 2, 'Indian Premier League', 'Statista Dossier about Indian Premier League (IPL)', '<p>This dossier presents insights and statistics about Indian Premier League. The Indian Premier League (IPL), is a professional Twenty20 cricket league in India contested during April and May of every year by teams representing Indian cities and some states. This dossier provides overview of sponsorship, viewership and cricket statistics of Indian Premier League from its inception in 2008.</p>', 365.00, 60, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 48, 1, '2019-06-06 06:10:43', '2019-06-06 06:22:27'),
(22, 1, 3, 'E-commerce worldwide', 'Statista dossier about e-commerce worldwide', '<p>This dossier presents statistics and facts on the global online retail e-commerce market. It includes data regarding the global e-commerce market volume as well as information on digital shoppers and consumer spending, as well as mobile commerce and digital payments.</p>', 365.00, 105, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 51, 1, '2019-06-06 06:11:34', '2019-06-06 06:24:32'),
(23, 1, 1, 'Cosmetics industry in the U.S.', 'Statista dossier on the cosmetics industry in the U.S.', '<p>This dossier provides statistical information regarding the cosmetics industry in the United States. The dossier is broken down into the following categories: a market overview of the U.S. cosmetic industry, structure of the cosmetic industry, retail sales and leading cosmetic companies.</p>', 365.00, 89, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 71, 1, '2019-06-06 06:12:22', NULL),
(24, 1, 1, 'Hotels Worldwide', 'Statista dossier on the global hotel industry', '<p>This dossier presents a range of statistics and facts about the global hotel industry. The study includes statistics on average daily rates (ADR), revenue per available room (RevPar), and occupancy rates for the hotel industry worldwide and in the United States. It also includes information on guest satisfaction and consumer opinion.</p>', 365.00, 83, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 55, 1, '2019-06-06 06:13:21', NULL),
(25, 1, 1, 'Mobile app monetization', 'Statista dossier about mobile app monetization', '<p>This dossier presents insights and statistics on mobile app monetization. It provides an overview of leading app store metrics as well as various forecasts regarding app revenue. The paper furthermore contains statistics on app stores, gaming apps, app buyers, and information on the most relevant trends.</p>', 365.00, 170, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 49, 1, '2019-06-06 06:14:31', NULL),
(26, 1, 1, 'YouTube', 'Statista dossier about YouTube', '<p>This dossier presents information on the online video portal YouTube. The paper provides benchmark comparisons regarding user metrics and user engagement as well as number of video streams. YouTube&#39;s reach and the subsequent usage in advertising and marketing are also explained.</p>', 365.00, 121, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 45, 1, '2019-06-06 06:15:14', NULL),
(27, 1, 1, 'Chocolate', 'Statista dossier on the chocolate industry', '<p>This dossier presents a range of statistics and facts about the chocolate industry.</p>', 365.00, 67, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 48, 1, '2019-06-06 06:15:50', NULL),
(28, 1, 1, 'Sporting goods in the United States', 'Statista dossier on the sporting goods industry', '<p>The dossier presents a range of statistics and facts on the U.S sporting goods market. The dossier includes chapters on the overview of the market, retail, wholesale, consumer behavior, shopping location preferences, and brand preferences.</p>', 365.00, 86, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 49, 1, '2019-06-06 06:16:38', NULL),
(29, 1, 1, 'Marriott International', 'Statista dossier on Marriott International', '<p>This dossier presents a range of statistics and facts on the hotel chain Marriott International. It includes information on the global hotel industry, revenue figures, number of properties and more.</p>', 365.00, 54, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 47, 1, '2019-06-06 06:17:26', NULL),
(30, 1, 1, 'Air transportation', 'Statista Dossier about air transportation', '<p>This dossier presents graphs and tables about air transportation in the U.S. and worldwide. Focusing on passenger transportation, it also provides data on air cargo and aviation safety data.</p>', 365.00, 77, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 51, 1, '2019-06-06 06:18:16', NULL),
(31, 1, 1, 'Personal computers (PCs)', 'Statista dossier on the global personal computer market', '<p>This dossier presents a range of statistics on the global PC market. The report covers worldwide personal computer shipments and the market share of major global vendors. It also incldudes statistics on spending on personal computers and other IT hardware associated with personal computers. Finally, the dossier also looks at the tablet computer market.</p>', 365.00, 68, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 46, 1, '2019-06-06 06:19:07', NULL),
(32, 1, 7, 'Tea market in the U.S.', 'Statista dossier on the tea market in the U.S.', '<p>This dossier provides statistical information about the U.S. tea market.</p>', 365.00, 74, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 58, 1, '2019-06-06 06:28:32', NULL),
(33, 1, 7, 'Marriott International', 'Statista dossier on Marriott International', '<p>This dossier presents a range of statistics and facts on the hotel chain Marriott International. It includes information on the global hotel industry, revenue figures, number of properties and more.</p>', 365.00, 54, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 57, 1, '2019-06-06 06:29:27', NULL),
(34, 1, 8, 'Adidas', 'Statista Dossier about Adidas', '<p>This dossier presents a range of statistics and facts about the Adidas Group, the leading supplier of athletic footwear and apparel in Germany and Europe and the second largest sportswear manufacturer in the world.</p>', 365.00, 91, 'English', '2019-06-06', '', 55, 1, '2019-06-06 06:30:10', NULL),
